summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 305E page 190 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Portion of Sec. 3-23-4, located in tract east of Empire Way and south of Roxbury St., from Single Family Residence Medium Density (RS 7200) Zone to General Commercial (CG) Zone.
